title: HOUR 2- Chip Kelly Sep 25, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 2- Chip Kelly Sep 25, 2020
description:
Coach Chip Kelly says he has not tail gated in a very very long time. Coach says Aaron Rodgers is the toughest QB he has ever faced. Coach tells Dan that he and his team wants to play and feels that 6 weeks is what is needed to get ready.
